# Summary
The Revenue LTV chart in Amplitude allows users on Growth and Enterprise plans to analyze new-user monetization over a 12-month period, tracking metrics like Total Revenue, New Paying Users, ARPU, and ARPPU, requiring proper revenue event tracking through Amplitude's SDKs or custom implementation.

